Apart from his legendary career, a great champion of civil rights, environmental protection and independent cinema, an opponent of Hollywood's drift, is now also going down the drain.
We have probably often seen him stand with his foot in bowls of vinaigrette, in sauces, pastries or other foods, and this considered quite tasteless, although we initially found it funny.
