Mercandelli also referred to "the progressive deterioration in the level of protection for victims of industrial accidents" and denounced "the abolition of the social system against which we have been fighting in recent years".
"The aim is therefore to return to the worker a guarantee on insurance, so that the fate of the victim of an accident at work does not depend on voluntary or accidental donations, decided from time to time by a legislator".
